ABBY: <i>Previously,</i>
<i>on </i>Dance Moms...

00:00:02.869 --> 00:00:04.371 line:5%,start
MAN (over the phone):
<i>(indistinct) this weekend has</i>
<i>been canceled.</i>

00:00:05.472 --> 00:00:07.340 line:5%,start
Oh, my God.

00:00:07.407 --> 00:00:08.842 line:5%,start
-Calm down, calm down.
-(sobs)

00:00:08.908 --> 00:00:10.310 line:5%,start
Nia...

00:00:10.377 --> 00:00:11.978 line:5%,start
Whatever. I'll pack my bags

00:00:12.045 --> 00:00:13.279 line:5%,start
and go home right now!

00:00:13.346 --> 00:00:15.315 line:5%,start
