-ANNOUNCER: <i>This is Maddie.</i>
-(cheers and applause)

00:00:19.753 --> 00:00:20.787 line:5%,start
ANNOUNCER: <i>Here we go.</i>

00:00:21.454 --> 00:00:22.856 line:5%,start
-(dramatic effect)
-JILL: Oh! I gotta go.

00:00:22.922 --> 00:00:24.591 line:5%,start
I don't want to make Abby mad.

00:00:24.657 --> 00:00:26.559 line:5%,start
ABBY: Jill, you have a big
decision to make.

00:00:26.626 --> 00:00:27.594 line:5%,start
Don't take it lightly.

00:00:27.660 --> 00:00:29.195 line:5%,start
I'll discuss it
with my daughter.

00:00:29.262 --> 00:00:30.563 line:5%,start
You know? What we come up with.

00:00:31.131 --> 00:00:32.799 line:5%,start
<i>That's just a little something.</i>

00:00:32.866 --> 00:00:34.100 line:5%,start
ABBY: <i>You know</i>
<i>everyone's going hate you</i>

00:00:34.167 --> 00:00:35.502 line:5%,start
-when they see that?
-I've got nothing to lose.

00:00:35.568 --> 00:00:36.403 line:5%,start
-(laughing)
-Right?

00:00:36.469 --> 00:00:38.004 line:5%,start
-CHRISTI: I think you should--
-You guys pick on me

00:00:38.071 --> 00:00:39.305 line:5%,start
'cause you push me out--

00:00:39.372 --> 00:00:40.874 line:5%,start
-I think because you're a
diva... -...that's what she
wants.

00:00:40.940 --> 00:00:41.841 line:5%,start
-...table for one.
-Oh.

00:00:41.908 --> 00:00:43.109 line:5%,start
ABBY: I have had it with you!

00:00:43.176 --> 00:00:44.044 line:5%,start
What is she saying?

00:00:44.110 --> 00:00:46.346 line:5%,start
ABBY: You didn't show up
the whole month to take class.

00:00:46.413 --> 00:00:48.148 line:5%,start
Your mother sits out
there and screams.

00:00:48.214 --> 00:00:50.016 line:5%,start
We come to Dance to dance,

00:00:50.083 --> 00:00:51.818 line:5%,start
and sitting there is not dance.

00:00:51.885 --> 00:00:52.719 line:5%,start
Go.

00:00:52.786 --> 00:00:54.320 line:5%,start
HOLLY: <i>And I think the guns are,</i>
<i>also as moms,</i>

00:00:54.387 --> 00:00:56.156 line:5%,start
it's throwing us off a bit.

00:00:56.222 --> 00:00:57.791 line:5%,start
I've done children with guns.

00:00:57.857 --> 00:00:59.959 line:5%,start
<i>That's what we entered,</i>
<i>that's what we're doing.</i>

00:01:00.026 --> 00:01:01.061 line:5%,start
(gunshot)

