00:38:58.936 --> 00:38:59.970 line:95%,end
ABBY: They looked
like they were in a show.

00:39:00.037 --> 00:39:01.339 line:95%,end
It was great.
-It was really good.

00:39:01.405 --> 00:39:02.573 line:95%,end
Don't your stomachs get full

00:39:02.640 --> 00:39:05.176 line:95%,end
