to their fullest potential.

00:39:17.488 --> 00:39:18.823 line:95%,end
Maybe Maddie was.

00:39:18.889 --> 00:39:21.792 line:95%,end
I know for a fact Kendall
wasn't used to her fullest
potential.

00:39:22.360 --> 00:39:24.929 line:95%,end
ABBY: <i>Jill is certainly</i>
<i>not learning from her mistakes.</i>

00:39:24.995 --> 00:39:29.467 line:95%,end
She comes at me in a combative
way, rips on my choreography.

00:39:29.900 --> 00:39:33.337 line:95%,end
Jill, butt out,
follow the rules,

00:39:33.404 --> 00:39:35.005 line:95%,end
and let me work with Kendall.

00:39:35.072 --> 00:39:37.842 line:95%,end
JILL: You were all excited
to give her a special part,

00:39:37.908 --> 00:39:39.844 line:95%,end
and there was no special part.

00:39:39.910 --> 00:39:42.880 line:95%,end
She did what everybody else did,
and less than some.

00:39:42.947 --> 00:39:45.116 line:95%,end
I think Jill's idea
of a special part

00:39:45.683 --> 00:39:48.953 line:95%,end
is everybody else stands
on stage and poses,

00:39:49.019 --> 00:39:50.721 line:95%,end
then Kendall dances
in the middle.

00:39:50.788 --> 00:39:53.758 line:95%,end
ABBY: Jill, Kendall
is a beautiful girl.

00:39:53.824 --> 00:39:55.359 line:95%,end
