00:39:59.296 --> 00:40:01.065 line:95%,end
That's a growing process.

00:40:01.132 --> 00:40:03.300 line:95%,end
It takes years to develop.

00:40:03.367 --> 00:40:05.770 line:95%,end
And I don't think you should
run your studio like that.

00:40:08.839 --> 00:40:12.243 line:95%,end
I produce employable,

00:40:12.309 --> 00:40:15.913 line:95%,end
