competition kids.

00:40:16.480 --> 00:40:18.849 line:95%,end
You need to keep your eye on the
ball in the big picture.

00:40:18.916 --> 00:40:20.217 line:95%,end
What is my big picture?

00:40:20.284 --> 00:40:23.087 line:95%,end
Every weekend,
do I have to look forward to
coming,

00:40:23.154 --> 00:40:25.222 line:5%,start
dancing behind Maddie and Chloe,

00:40:25.289 --> 00:40:28.426 line:5%,start
and never being put in a trio,
never doing the solo?

00:40:28.492 --> 00:40:29.960 line:5%,start
I get nothing, Abby!

00:40:30.027 --> 00:40:32.029 line:5%,start
You're telling me look
at the big picture.

00:40:32.096 --> 00:40:33.697 line:5%,start
And I am, and I don't like it!

00:40:33.764 --> 00:40:34.799 line:5%,start
ABBY: <i>I don't know.</i>

00:40:34.865 --> 00:40:36.700 line:5%,start
I don't know what
is wrong with her.

00:40:37.067 --> 00:40:39.270 line:5%,start
<i>It's going to all shake out</i>
<i>in the wash for Kendall,</i>

00:40:39.336 --> 00:40:40.971 line:5%,start
